Package: attempt
Title: A Friendlier Condition Handler
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Colin", "Fay", email = "contact@colinfay.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A friendlier condition Handler for R, inspired by 'purrr' mappers and based on 'rlang'.
    attempt allows you to handle conditions easily, and offers a consistant grammar throughout all 
    the package functions.
